{"tid":2365882,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 3 月在日本舉行線上演唱會！即日起開始售票","createTime":"2021-01-14T05:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T11:48:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"43fb28ba09757937d77839750aa006c02c96f825","tid":2365882,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_9edb35f11dd4ea797c89769fb1c41414/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-14/132997-893299.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_9edb35f11dd4ea797c89769fb1c41414%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-14%2F132997-893299.png&h=fb25f3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在《Beyond LIVE - TWICE : World in A Day》結束半年多後，TWICE 又將在線上舉行演唱會啦！<br />\n<br />\n日本華納音樂今天（14 日）宣布 TWICE 將於 3 月 6 日晚間 7 點（日本時間），在線上舉行《TWICE in Wonderland》演唱會，並透過當地的「新體感 LIVE CONNECT Special Live」獨家直播。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_49fd75d27c6d82e2e2439b8faabeea9e/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-14/132997-893300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_49fd75d27c6d82e2e2439b8faabeea9e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-14%2F132997-893300.jpg&h=fcf19c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新體感 LIVE CONNECT Special Live 透露：「TWICE 將藉由『另一個 TWICE 世界』，來實現無法於 2020 年在日本舉行的演唱會。」TWICE 原定於去年 3 月登上日東京巨蛋開唱，可惜幾經延期後仍因疫情而宣告取消。儘管如此，一整年內在當地推出四張作品的她們仍展現了強烈的存在感。<br />\n<br />\n《TWICE in Wonderland》將結合最新技術提供即時的演唱會直播，屆時無論透過電腦、手機或傳輸到電視上皆可觀看，ONCE 別忘了提早做好準備囉！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"077cd1d437c625879e73d2dada088560559daf68","tid":2365882,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"新體位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎預購入場券睇我同Mina 彩瑛嘅性愛表演<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset